<p>
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SRC Travel Agencies is the agency that provides the transportation facility to the 
customers based on their requirements.</br>
We provide different buses like Express, 
Luxury,and Volvo (Has two types A/C and Non A/C).</br>
The charges are different for different buses. The charges are in the below mentioned format. 
</p>
<p
    Express < Luxury < Volvo (Non A/C) < Volvo (A/C) 
</p>
<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Charges also depend on the distance the customer wants to travel and as well on 
the age of the customer.</br>
- Up to the age of 5 years there will not be any charges.</br>
- In between 5-12 there will be half charges.</br>
- For above 12 the charges will be full till the age of 50</br>
- For the age above fifty they will get a discount of 30%.</br>
</p>
<p>
Also for canceling the ticket, there is a limit like:</br>
- If cancelled before 2 days, the whole money will be returned.</br>
- If done one day before, 85% is refunded.</br>
- If done on that day, 70% is refunded.</br>
</p>
